xt-stroke">Top Soft Candy Manufacturer &amp; Supplier Since 1991</h1><div id="brxe-ctuwnb" class="brxe-divider horizontal"><div class="line"></div></div><div id="brxe-iumqar" class="brxe-text-basic">LeChao is a veteran soft candy manufacturer, focusing on the production, customization and wholesale of gummy candies, sour strips, marshmallows, chocolate candies, etc. Empowering you to establish private label candy brand.</div><div id="brxe-xkukmt" class="brxe-block bricks-lazy-hidden"><a id="brxe-mpativ" class="brxe-button bricks-button bricks-background-primary" href="https://www.lechaocandy.com/wholesale-candy-supplier/">All Candy Category</a><button id="brxe-tuatzo" class="brxe-button bricks-button bricks-background-secondary" data-interactions="[{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;xjxqvy&quot;,&quot;trigger&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;show&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;popup&quot;,&quot;templateId&quot;:&quot;28&quot;}]" data-interaction-id="f3dde5">Talk To Team</button></div></div></div></div><div id="brxe-zamnsw" class="brxe-block home_banner_ratio bricks-lazy-hidden"><div id="brxe-vedavv" class="brxe-block home_banner_ratio bricks-lazy-hidden"><div id="brxe-iaiuzu" class="brxe-div bricks-lazy-hidden" data-interactions="[{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;oltkyd&quot;,&quot;trigger&quot;:&quot;enterView&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;startAnimation&quot;,&quot;animationType&quot;:&quot;slideInRight&quot;,&quot;animationDuration&quot;:&quot;1.5s&quot;}]" data-interaction-id="6a9214" data-interaction-hidden-on-load="1"><h2 id="brxe-saddsw" class="brxe-heading white-text-stroke">Your Trusted Custom Soft Candy Manufacturer</h2><div id="brxe-wtmrev" class="brxe-divider horizontal"><div class="line"></div></div><div id="brxe-mmccgs" class="brxe-text-basic">Lechao offers expert OEM/ODM services for soft candy with 500+ molds, catering to supermarkets, wholesalers, and retailers. We specialize in creating unique flavors, shapes, and packaging to elevate your brand.</div><di