quot;:&quot;mouseenter&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;setAttribute&quot;,&quot;actionAttributeKey&quot;:&quot;data-bg&quot;,&quot;actionAttributeValue&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;custom&quot;,&quot;targetSelector&quot;:&quot;.con-hover-item-change-bg&quot;}]" data-interaction-id="d57d2d"><div id="brxe-756371" class="brxe-div item-info bricks-lazy-hidden"><h2 id="brxe-002710" class="brxe-heading pricolor-text-stroke">02</h2><h3 id="brxe-33eaec" class="brxe-heading item-info-title pricolor-text-stroke">Strict Food Safety Control</h3><div id="brxe-f5a05c" class="brxe-block item-info-detail bricks-lazy-hidden"><div id="brxe-ac6df5" class="brxe-text-basic">From raw material selection, production control to factory inspection, we follow international food safety standards and are safe and traceable.</div><a id="brxe-0200e4" class="brxe-button transparent-btn bricks-button" href="https://www.lechaocandy.com/candy-manufacturing-capability/">Our Manufacturing Capability</a></div></div></div><div id="brxe-155fa5" class="brxe-block item bricks-lazy-hidden" data-interactions="[{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;bkgmaj&quot;,&quot;trigger&quot;:&quot;mouseenter&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;setAttribute&quot;,&quot;actionAttributeKey&quot;:&quot;data-bg&quot;,&quot;actionAttributeValue&quot;:&quot;3&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;custom&quot;,&quot;targetSelector&quot;:&quot;.con-hover-item-change-bg&quot;}]" data-interaction-id="36a225"><div id="brxe-146df2" class="brxe-div item-info bricks-lazy-hidden"><h2 id="brxe-acf274" class="brxe-heading pricolor-text-stroke">03</h2><h3 id="brxe-5c04dd" class="brxe-heading item-info-title pricolor-text-stroke">One-Stop Export Support</h3><div id="brxe-bb9af6" class="brxe-block item-info-detail bricks-lazy-hidden"><div id="brxe-01192b" class="brxe-text-basic">From formula testing, outer packaging design, language labeling, local regulatory compliance to international logistics arrangements, LeChao provides full support.
</div><button id="brxe-9867df" class="brxe-button transparent-btn bricks-button" data-interactions="[{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;lrwshq&quot;,&quot;trigger&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;show&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;popup&quot;,&quot;templateId&quot;:&quot;28&quot;}]" data-interaction-id="b7c138">Partner With LeChao</button></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-wpr-lazyrender="1" id="brxe-vnqelx" class="brxe-section bricks-lazy-hidden"><div  id="brxe-utczvd" class="brxe-container bricks-lazy-hidden"><h2 id="brxe-qvsqsq" class="brxe-heading">Why do 500+ Clients Join Hands with LeChao?</h2><div id="brxe-ylirtm" class="brxe-block bricks-lazy-hidden"><div id="brxe-cmmuve" class="brxe-block bricks-lazy-hidden"><h2 id="brxe-phzpli" class="brxe-heading">Excellent Reputation</h2><div id="brxe-zrenfa" class="brxe-text-basic">Our wholesale candies have been market-proven and well received by customers.</div></div><div id="brxe-bfamxn" class="brxe-block bricks-lazy-hidden"><h2 id="brxe-gohomu" class="brxe-heading">Global Certification</h2><div id="brxe-lqzszv" class="brxe-text-basic">Support HACCP, FDA, ISO, Halal and other certifications, in line with international standards.</div></div><div id="brxe-jfnbbg" class="brxe-block bricks-lazy-hidden"><h2 id="brxe-shvvsr" class="brxe-heading">Powerful R&D</h2><div id="brxe-lgrdqc" class="brxe-text-basic">Self-developed molds 500+, we can provide OEM/ODM services and free samples for you.</div></div><div id="brxe-qfgnmc" class="brxe-block bricks-lazy-hidden"><h2 id="brxe-vqnwaa" class="brxe-heading">Efficient Manufacturing</h2><div id="brxe-hctnkx" class="brxe-text-basic">80% automated production, 24-hour continuous operation, to ensure efficient and stable supply.</div></div><div id="brxe-iydppc" class="brxe-block bricks-lazy-hidden"><h2 id="brxe-xcdpzc" class="brxe-heading">High Cost Performance</h2><div id="brxe-uvphpm" class="brxe-text-basic">Relying on strong production capacity, we can provide you with very competitive purchase prices.</div></div><div id="brxe-gogtjw" class="brxe-block bricks-lazy-hidden"><h2 id="brxe-kvwonr" class="brxe-heading">Reliable Supply Chain</h2><div id="brxe-ciujow" class="brxe-text-basic">Ensure efficient logistics and timely delivery to meet the supermarket, retail, and bulk needs of different markets.</div></div></div></div></section><section data-wpr-lazyrender="1" id="brxe-ppkhwp" class="brxe-section bricks-lazy-hidden"><div  id="brxe-ayxrrh" class="brxe-container bricks-lazy-hidden"><h2 id="brxe-scpxaz" class="brxe-heading">Blog & News</h2><div id="brxe-hpgjxq" class="brxe-text-basic">We share the latest candy industry trends, product innovations, and market insights, with regular updates on manufacturing, consumer preferences, and LeChao news.</div><div id="brxe-hgmqhi" data-script-id="hgmqhi" class="brxe-slider-nested bricks-lazy-hidden splide brx-auto-height" data-splide="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;slide&quot;,&quot;direction&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;,&quot;keyboard&quot;:&quot;global&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;0px&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;perPage&quot;:3,&quot;perMove&quot;:1,&quot;speed&quot;:400,&quot;interval&quot;:3000,&quot;autoHeight&quot;:true,&quot;autoplay&quot;:false,&quot;pauseOnHover&quot;:false,&quot;pauseOnFocus&quot;:false,&quot;arrows&quot;:true,&quot;pagination&quot;:false,&quot;mediaQuery&quot;:&quot;max&quot;,&quot;breakpoints&quot;:{&quot;2560&quot;:{&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;50px&quot;,&quot;perPage&quot;:&quot;3&quot;},&quot;1520&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;slide&quot;,&quot;autoHeight&quot;:true,&quot;arrows&quot;:true},&quot;767&quot;:{&quot;perPage&quot;:&quot;2&quot;},&quot;478&quot;:{&quot;perPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}}}"><div class="splide__track"><div class="splide__list"><template style='display:none' aria-hidden='true' data-brx-loop-start='uujyiw'></template><div class="brxe-uujyiw brxe-block bricks-lazy-hidden"><a href="https://www.lechaocandy.com/pee